Hiking style 
==============

These are the CartoCSS map stylesheets for the lucadelu hiking style

Prerequisites
=================

Software
-----------

* cartocss
* Mapnik
* PostGIS

Data
--------
* OpenStreetMap data loaded in PostGIS database called `osm` with prefix name planet_osm
* contour lines loadded in PostGIS database called `osm` with table name contour
* a hillshade raster file called `hillshade.tif` located in `layers` folder
* a slope raster called `slope.tif` located in `layers` folder
* a relief raster called `relief.tif` located in `layers` folder

This tree rasters can be created using gdaldem software

